#. type: Plain text
#: data/man/locale-tester.1:8
msgid ""
"B<locale-tester> is a GTK4/Adwaita application for inspecting and comparing "
"system locale settings on Linux. It displays dates, time, numbers, currency, "
"percent, collation order, weekday and month names, decimal and thousands "
"separators, allows side-by-side locale comparison, includes a strftime "
"tester, and shows LC_* environment variable overview."
msgstr ""

